summaries.short: Precious Ramotswe looks into the cases of a frightened shopkeeper, a two o'clock doctor, and a possible poisoning.
summaries.full: Precious visits a local orphanage, where a young woman tells her she's worried about her father who seems unusually fearful. A new client, Dr. Sibenke, asks Precious to investigate the mysterious deaths of three patients under his care, who each died on a Friday at 2 o'clock. Later, a wealthy landowner hires her to investigate a suspected poisoning in his family.

titles.full: The Boy with an African Heart

summaries.short: Precious investigates the case of an American who has been missing for over ten years.
summaries.full: An American woman, Andrea Curtin, comes to the agency looking for her son who disappeared 10 years earlier. Grace asks for a promotion; BK finds his salon ransacked; and Precious and Andrea discover that a woman named Clara may be involved in the case of 'The Boy with an African Heart.' Later, Grace reveals a long-held secret to Precious.

summaries.short: Precious investigates the mysteries of a disturbed dentist, a disappearing dog and a missing husband.
summaries.full: When a young boy named Wellington comes into the agency looking for work, Precious hires him to hand out flyers. Meanwhile, Precious checks out a Nigerian dentist who has suspicious mood swings; helps a worried man, Rre Banda, in his search for his missing dog; and stumbles upon the case of a missing husband.

summaries.short: The Agency looks into a stolen sedan, a cheating wife, and a secretly-dating daughter.
summaries.full: Mma Pekwane comes to the agency fearing that her husband has purchased a stolen car. Patel, a local electronics-store owner, asks Precious to investigate whether his daughter has a secret boyfriend. JLB uses a 'high-tech' solution to help Precious with the 'Steal Stolen Sedan' for the Lord case. Grace dives into her new assistant-detective role

summaries.short: Precious and Grace stave off competition while investigating a case of badly behaved beauty queens.
summaries.full: Precious and Grace learn of a rival agency and decide to check out the competition. A beauty-pageant promoter asks Precious to vet the contestants in his Beauty and Integrity contest. Patel asks Precious to ramp up her investigation of Nandira, his daughter. Meanwhile, when JLB goes away, Precious discovers that absence makes the heart grow fonder.
